# Videos Directory

This directory will contain demo videos for CloudSecure AI.

## Required Videos:
- demo-thumbnail.png (1280x720)
- platform-demo.mp4 (1920x1080, 3-5 minutes)

## Video Guidelines:
1. Record at 30fps for smooth playback
2. Include clear narration or subtitles
3. Show real application functionality
4. Keep duration under 5 minutes
5. Use professional screen recording software

## Content Structure:
1. Introduction (30s)
2. Dashboard Tour (1m)
3. Account Setup (1m)
4. Security Scan (1m)
5. AI Chat Demo (1m)
6. Conclusion (30s)
